m- silky smooth mouthfeel, the head adds a velvet like feel to the tart flavors. Exactly what I expected.
o- this has been the best brett saison I have had. Ever. Top five beers of all time for me thus far. 938 charactersSFACRKnight, Nov 30, 2012
